(1521, 48, 'Simulation: What happens here? try { con = DriverManager.getConnection(url, user, pass); } catch(SQLException e) { e.printStackTrace(); } d. Nothing', '', 'Prints stack trace if connection fails', 'Automatically retries connection', 'Commits transaction', 'A', 'Intermediate', 'Quiz question'),
