(1580, 49, 'Simulation: What does this code do? try { throw new IOException(\"File error\"); } catch(IOException e) { throw new RuntimeException(\"Wrapped exception\", e); } d. Does nothing', '', 'Wraps IOException into RuntimeException', 'Suppresses exception', 'Handles exception silently', 'A', 'Intermediate', 'Quiz question'),
