(1848, 30, 'Responsive Two-Column Layout Create a two-column layout using CSS. When the screen width is less than 600px, make it change into one column using media queries.', '', '', '', '', 'A', 'Intermediate', 'Simulation question'),
(1849, 30, 'CSS Transitions Create a button that changes color smoothly when hovered. Use the transition property to animate: Background color Text color Add a 0.5s transition duration.', '', '', '', '', 'A', 'Intermediate', 'Simulation question'),
(1850, 30, 'CSS Transformations Create a square box that: Rotates 45 degrees on hover using transform: rotate() Scales up slightly when hovered. Combine both effects for animation.', '', '', '', '', 'A', 'Intermediate', 'Simulation question'),
